attributes.review:
I downloaded this app which took about 2 hours to install, I was traumatized by an explicit photo of a wrinkly hairless rat holding up a tubby fist, and it continuously crashed my phone. My phone was attacked with hateful messages in support of racism, fascism, bigotry, child molestation, homophobia, transphobia, xenophobia, and misogyny just to name a few!!! I did not even approve of receiving notifications!! This app is fake news. I will forever be haunted by the explicit images of a soggy Cheeto puff- ruined my enjoyment of that snack by the way. Would not recommend to a friend. This app spreads hatred easier than the coronavirus. Please remove from the App Store. 
XOXO Gen Z girl
